house_rules.aditional:
Pool and gym access is on the 5th floor. Exit left from lifts. please observe rules and times, no eating or drinking in the area, and please be modest on the way and returning from pool.


Rubbish.
Please put all recycle material in the bins downstairs....opposite lift doors. This includes glass and plastic bottles and paper and cardboard.

Use the garbage chute on the 12th floor for kitchen rubbish only. No heavy items please as they can damage the chute.

location_descriptions.title: Neighbourhood highlights
location_descriptions.content:
The area is an oasis of quiet so close to the city, with a great shopping precinct (DFO) nearby, the Yarra river and marina a short stroll and good selection of grocery stores. it's next to Marvel Stadium and major corporate head offices with great pubs and restaurants nearby. 5min walk to Southern Cross Station and tram stop 2 min walk. The tram stop is within the free tram network so no ticket is required if travelling within the CBD.
A park with basketball courts and fitness track is opposite and can be utilised by guests.

location_descriptions.title: Getting around
location_descriptions.content: Ample 2hr free parking and many metered car parks, free parking from 6.30pm till 7am on most streets. Very close to all public transport and car share available at base of building.

description:
Enjoy your stay in melbourne with a complete experience in the city with access to a pool, spa, sauna and gym. You have your own balcony with a bbq and suround sound with a 65 in TV. Smeg and Bosch appliances and nespresso coffee machine, all you need for a tranquil and enjoyable stay.

The space
Very cosy and uniquely decorated

Guest access
Guests can use the outdoor swimming pool, sauna, spa and gym located on the 5th floor.

Other things to note
After a long trip by plane, car or public transport its hard to get supplies so; fresh milk, water, tea & coffee and some breakfast items are included for your stay.
title: Newly renovated. Stylish apartment with balcony.

reviews.comments: Livio is a great host. The apartment felt like a home and was in a great location. Check in was extremely easy. We will be staying here whenever we are in melbourne, can’t recommend it enough.
Highly recommend this place. Livio was an excellent host and nothing was a problem. Helpful local advice. The flat was very clean and well maintained and, most importantly, it felt like home.
This is my second time choosing Livio’s place to stay—another awesome experience. Thank you, Livio!

Livio's place was nothing short of a haven for my stay. It's very walkable, with a tram stop that takes you to the heart of the city 2 minutes away. Southern Cross is also right there, about a 10 minute walk but makes for super easy check in if you're flying. Bed was super comfortable, and he'd left a few snack/ breakfast things available for me as well which made the morning after I landed really convenient. Will absolutely book here again next time I need something central Melbourne.

Livio's place was perfect for our Melbourne stay. The location was just what we wanted and it was a huge bonus being so close to trams, the SkyBus and Southern Cross station. The apartment was very clean, quiet, well equipped and very comfortable. We couldn't fault a thing.

My partner and I had a wonderful stay at Livio’s apartment. The location was incredibly convenient, and the kitchen was well-equipped with everything we needed, including a thoughtful selection of breakfast items. The apartment was spotless, easy to access, and Livio was always responsive and helpful throughout our stay. It was definitely one of the best Airbnbs we've experienced!

Livio's place was comfortable and very clean.
A number of additional food items were provided, however the lace curtains were a bit unneeded as they interrupted the good views from all the windows.
The bedroom became quite warm quickly in the morning which was unexpected.
The apartment was close to 45, 11 trams to go down Collins St getting into the CBD which was great.
overall a pleasant and convenient location provided a good stay.
Amazing location - walking distance to South Bank etc - highly recommended!

7 days here. One of the best Airbnb apartments we’ve ever been in. Kitchen is really well stocked.  Everything you ever need for cooking. Comfortable bed.   Very clean apartment. Great location next door to the Marvel Stadium.  Nice balcony. We’d come back here anytime! Host very responsive, and had some nice goodies waiting for us when we checked in.
Great location, very clean.  Enjoyed the balcony, air conditioning, and breakfast supplies Livio left for us. Appartment was very quiet - never heard a neighbour.
Amazing Airbnb - home away from home in the heart of Docklands. Will stay again next work trip thanks!

Great place to stay, easy walk to trams, Marvel / Docklands and to the Southern Cross train station.
Lovely little apartment with all the amenities you could think of. Great communication and we were very grateful for the fruit / bread / cereal / milk and coffee and other nice touches that were left for us, thank you!
Would recommend and stay again.

This is one of the best AirBnB places I've stayed in ... a very classy home away from home with fantastic amenities. Livio was very proactive and helpful. The apartment was beautiful and comfortable with so many extras included.
My two key criteria for choosing a place for our stay were air con and a pool. This apartment had both - the air con was a godsend in the Melbourne heat wave, as was the stunning pool where we spent several afternoons.
It's also ideally situated for catching the most useful trams and walking distance from the Spenser St station.
Absolutely loved the place and very grateful that Livio was able to accommodate our request for an extra night, as we decided to stay on another night rather than move to the place we had booked near the airport for our final night in Melbourne.
Will most certainly be back!
It was a comfortable, spacious, private apartment in a good area. I felt right at home, and Livio was a great host. I would recommend it.
Great flat great host!

Our stay here was great! We were able to check in early which was amazing as our flight landed early in the morning. The apartment had everything we needed and the breakfast food which was left was very good! The apartment was in a perfect location to walk to lots of places in the city and there is a tram stop just across the road. It was very clean, would highly recommend this place!!

localizedReview.comments:
This is the best place to stay in Tsegwon! Really great!
I had a happy trip thanks to the friendly response and help!

reviews.comments: Very communicative host! Would recommend :)
One of the best places I have stayed at. Perfect location, quiet, full amenities, spotless clean, and everything you need. Amazing host. I highly recommend this place if visiting Melbourne.

The apartment was perfect for our needs (couple). Excellent location, just a few minutes walk to Southern Cross Station. Lots of eateries, supermarkets in walking distance. Fabulous outdoor swimming pool.
Lots of goodies left for us to enjoy.
Would highly recommend

Amazing location, beautiful apartment. Felt right as home, extremely clean, bed was very comfortable. Host provided breakfast foods and fruits as well as milk & two types of coffees. All the instructions were super easy to follow and location was very quiet.

Livio is an excellent host. The apartment is spotless, and the selection of breakfast items available is fantastic.
We will be back again!

We really enjoyed our stay. The towels were especially nice and there were thoughtful touches. We also had a great view of the fireworks at Marvel Stadium when Coldplay was playing - which was unexpected. Very convenient location. Would book again!
Located in the heart of the city, this place was perfect for our one week getaway. The apartment was spotless and beautifully decorated. Livio went above and beyond to make sure we felt at home.
Really enjoyed our time here it was very nice and clean and well looked after, Livio was very helpful and friendly, would stay again

A great place to stay in Melbourne! I stayed for two weeks and enjoyed every minute. A perfect location for walking into the City or down to the Docklands. The apartment was clean, modern and had everything I could have possibly needed.

Great place when u have a vacation in Mel. Good location (near train and tran station), good quality for everything in the flat and awesome host ; )
Livio’s place is super cozy and clean. I recommend staying in his place!

Livio is a fantastic host & we felt right at home at his place. The apartment itself is very modern, but also warm and full of charm. Situated in a perfect location for accessing the city & free tram, also in a fairly quiet part of town.
On arrival there was already a wonderful selection of breakfast foods waiting, including plenty of fruit, breads, brie & other delightful snacks! The kitchen is also very well appointed. We found the apartment very clean & cozy as others have said. We found the bed to be very comfortable.
Check-in relatively straight forward, really good instructions. We also appreciated that there was flexibility upon checking out. A really great stay & truly great host!

Thank you to Livio for presenting such a charming, characterful property, such a warm and welcoming space and so refreshing compared to the frequent corporate blandness that one often encounters. Livio was very proactive with his communication and had stocked the property with a wide range of goodies. Before arrival, he even asked what type of milk we preferred. We can most strongly recommend both the property and its host. Thanks loads Livio!

Great location next to the circle tram and Collins St tram. Tram is free inside the circle. We attended a convention at the MCC and were able to ride trams to the entrance without any problem despite the fact that the MCC is one stop out of the free tram zone. If you come in on the Skybus from the airport just walk to the Collins St tram stop next to he Batman Hill Hotel and get on tram that goes straight down Colliins St past the train station. i think that the tram number is 11. Pizza Hut is directly under the apartment on the street level. Livio left some groceries and milk in the refrigerator along with some fruit. It was very nice. Thank you, Livio.

We had a weekend stay at Livo's apartment for our anniversary celebration and it was beautiful, warming, modern, homely, great views of city & Marvel stadium and a private location. We were able to walk to the football, city centre & Southbank for all our activities. Livo is a proactive, polite & professional host.

Livio has been an amazing guest. He’s been so dedicated to make sure everything was going smoothly for us. He went to bought breakfast for us and was extremely flexible with the arrival and departure time. We really appreciate that.
The place is really comfortable and comes with everything you need including gym and swimming pool facilities. The area is quiet with a nice buildings view and very well located to the city.
Thanks for making our stay comfortable

Perfect apartment for my stay whilst working at the convention centre. Great location. Well appointed to feel like coming ‘home’ after work. Very clean, comfortable and lots of nice little extra touches that made all the difference … nice lighting, groceries supplied, speakers connected ready for me to walk in and say ‘hey Google play radio ABC Jazz, string blinds that allowed the city lights to peak in but still have privacy. Livio was a wonderful, generous, thoughtful, communicative host. I hope to be able to stay again next time I’m in Melbourne.
Prefect option for Dockland and all city options
Great place to stay, especially if you have to stay for a longer period of time. Felt like a home away from home. Livio is a star; very helpful and easy to communicate with. Highly recommended.

Honestly the best host I’ve ever come across! I had to book last minute because of an emergency and Livio was so kind to meet me within the same hour of the inquiry, he also allowed me to view the apartment to make me feel safe and comfortable. The moment I walked in, I felt like I had entered paradise. I felt right at home. It is the most peaceful and luxurious airbnb that I’ve ever stayed at! Everything was perfect and Livio was super considerate— I wish I could extent! The only problem that you’ll have is that you wouldn’t want to leave. The place has such a lovely energy to it, I loved the fact that I could connect the speakers in every room to my devices. I also loved that it was so private— 0 disturbances and I slept like a baby every night! I would definitely book again and I cannot recommend Livio as a host enough! Thank you so much for an incredible experience :)

We booked this apartment for 2 nights and had a fantastic stay. It's roomy, spotlessly clean, views of the CBD with a nice balcony. The building's gym and pool are top-notch. Livio was a terrific host, great communicator, flexible and supplied us with great provisions.

Great place to stay! Perfect location near Docklands for my husband and son to attend the Formula One event. Livio was fantastic to communicate with and the apartment was clean and tidy with some lovely welcome gifts (great after a late night check in). Thanks Livio!

We had the best time in the apartment. Located near southern cross and within the free tram zone gave us all the flexibility we needed. Livio was a great host and even left us snacks, milk and other treats for breakfast when we arrived. Everything was clean and we immediately felt like home. The pool was also great for swimming and we couldn’t imagine a better place to cool down on hot days after work / sight seeing. We can fully recommend staying there when in Melbourne!

We very much enjoyed our stay at Livio's apartment! it was easy to check in to and in a great location not far from trams. The place was very tidy and had all the amenities you would need on holiday plus some food was supplied adding a nice touch. The host was very responsive through messages and was even flexible with check in and check out. We would highly recommend to anyone staying in the CBD and would stay here again!
Thank you Livio for being a fantastic host and the apartment was fabulous!
Such a beautiful apartment! Close to the tram, has everything you need and then some. Perfect for a comfortable stay :)

Livio’s home is the perfect balance of perfectly appointed and a comfortable home away from home.  It had everything I needed and more.  Livio was very welcoming and great communication throughout.  This is my new ‘must stay’ for future trips.
My partner and I had a lovely stay at Livios place! Was beautifully decorated and we were welcomed with bread, cheeses and other food. Would recommended to anyone who is thinking of staying.
この部屋はとても綺麗でおしゃれでした！私達は快適に過ごすことができました！年末のカウントダウンイベントが近くで行われます。Marvel Stadiumも徒歩です。とてもよい場所です！

localizedReview.comments: This place was very beautiful and stylish!We had a comfortable stay!The year-end countdown event will be held nearby.Marvel Stadium is also on foot.Great place!

reviews.comments: My husband and I stayed 2 months at Livio’s place. The apartment was pristine and perfect. Honestly I cannot think of a single thing I would add. Livio is also incredible and very responsive. He met me with a kind and robust welcome gift. Thank you so much Livio for a wonderful stay!

Livio was there to greet on arrival.
Explained everything.
Home was very clean
Thoroughly enjoyed our stay.

Absolutely fabulous! Livio is a super Superhost! The apartment was private, quite unique, and beautifully furnished while being really comfortable. There are too many extras to mention that Livio provided, but having enough coffee, fresh muffins and spreads, fruit, cereal, and milk for the first few days was a fantastic start to our 11 night stay. The location was brilliant, and 5 minutes walk to the free zone city trams. It's easily the best Airbnb experience we've had.

Thanks Livio. I really enjoyed staying in your apartment. It's a beautiful, clean and tidy home. I had everything I needed and it's a cozy and comfortable place. It was lovely to see complementary food basket and fridge having various types of milk and drinks. I would highly recommend this place! Thanks again

This apartment was terrific - clean, comfortable, beautifully decorated and equipped with everything you need. The bed was comfortable and the bathroom was clean and modern. The kitchen was clean and well appointed with good cookware, utensils and crockery. It was a lovely surprise to have fresh bread, milk, fruit and other items provided on arrival.
Livio is a great host - very responsive and helpful. He's thought of everything to make my stay comfortable and enjoyable. Thankyou Livio!

Beautiful apartment, perfect 4 day getaway.
We will definitely return.
Wonderful location, great food, shopping and bars.
great access to Marvel stadium and free tram service.
Livio was amazing, the space was beautiful and located so conveniently. 100% coming back!
The apartment was cosy and had everything we needed for the stay. Livio was very accomodating and friendly. Close to public transport and shops. Would recommend for anyone visiting melbourne.

Our stay was everything we could've asked for ! great communication through Livio. Location was great with 5mins walking distance to the train station as well as trams. The place was spotless and had a modern feel to it. Perfect stay for 2 people or even on your own. Would highly recommend

Wow ! Is all I can say. This was the best Airbnb experience I’ve ever had. Livio is such a great host, so helpful and made me feel right at home. The apartment surpassed my expectations, the cleanliness and attention to detail was second to none. I love all the thoughtful added extras that Livio provided for example food, fruit, travel card and so many options to make you feel comfortable. The apartment was fantastic, beautiful touches of luxury. Highly highly recommended. Will definitely be staying again.
Livio was a fantastic host. The apartment is fantastic and in a great location with lots of public transport and shops within walking distance. Would definitely stay there again.

Amazing apartment, clean and sizable for the price with all the amenities. Livio has been an amazing host, nice enough to meet up and give us a tour and went above and beyond to make sure our stay was great. 11/10.

Livio’s place worked out perfectly for me. It’s stocked with everything that you need and a bit more. The location is convenient and close to public transport. Livio is a great host and I’m glad I picked his place to stay.

The apartment was perfect for our needs. It was spacious, clean, comfortable and had lots of thoughtful additions that made the stay so easy.
Livio was a great host and so responsive.
Couldn't fault it. We will be back.

Livio was a fabulous host and we loved our stay. The thoughtful touches were so appreciated. Towels and linen were beautiful. Flexible check in after a delayed flight and Livio greeted us and gave us a good run down on everything we needed to know. Livio was so helpful and understanding and gave us some great recommendations for brunch.  The location on the map doesn’t do justice to how central and convenient this apartment is - everything we needed within a very short walk or tram ride. Thank you so much for having us!

The apartment is amazing! Beautiful view of the city, nice terrace with BBQ, terrific swimming pool and gym!
The apartment is located in the free tram zone so you can move through the city without paying anything and it's walk distance to the southern cross station, the ferries and the Marvel Stadium.
Livio is a wonderful host, super kind and friendly and always available!
I lived here during my first month in Australia and it has been great!!

Livio made the stay a wonderful and relaxing experience, thanks to his hospitality, interior decor panache, approachability, and responsiveness. On more than one occasion Livio went out of his way to assist me in preparing for and managing our stay throughout. We stayed for a month thanks to the Air BnB discount Livio offered for such a long stay, which made it possible to enjoy a some memorable holiday times living in Docklands.
It's a nice convenient apartment, well stocked with amenities including laundry and a nice balcony and easy to clean barbeque, with easy access to the on-site pool and gym, local city tram and Metro train network, boat cruises and nice local cafes.
If I could visit again another month then I'd not hesitate to book this apartment from Livio.
Very nice owner and apartment, will recommend to friends and will come again. Beautiful
Livio has the best style and his place is an absolute gem! Looking forward to staying there again soon!
reviews.response: Thanks Kellis, it was a pleasure to have you there, thanks for taking care if the place. Hope to have you again.
